race.description: Ladbrokes Fast Payouts Maiden Final F
race.comment: JUNGLE GYM (2) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 0.8 lengths from JACK'S DOUBLED in second (17.87) at this track. Can measure up this time. PRINCE TOMMY (5) hit the ground running off the tricky draw last start and was never headed (17.77) at this track in a Maiden over 324m. One of main contenders. JACK'S DOUBLED (6) proved too good on debut over 324m at this track to score by 0.8 lengths (17.81). This tougher but expected to be in the finish. CLASSIC TEARS (1) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.
